2. I&#039;m using Language Switcher, so i&#039;ve replaced &quot;$tag = str_replace(&#039; &#039;, &#039;&amp;nbsp;&#039;, wp_specialchars( $tag ));&quot; with &quot;$tag = apply_filters(&#039;the_title&#039;, str_replace(&#039; &#039;, &#039;&amp;nbsp;&#039;, wp_specialchars( $tag )));&quot;. Probably, this could be done in more elegant way, i dont know. </p>
<p>Thank you!-)</p>
				
				<p>
									</p>
		
		</div>
		
