		<li id="comment-4075">
		
		<div class="commentcont">
							
			<p>Okay this was an easy fix. </p>
<p>Change the whole *if (&#039;yes&#039; == $showcats) {* block to: </p>
<p>if (&#039;yes&#039; == $showcats) {<br />
// Do they want to see empty categories?<br />
if (&#039;yes&#039; == $empty) {<br />
$empty=0;<br />
} else {<br />
$empty=1;<br />
} </p>
<p>$hide_empty = &#039;&amp;hide_empty=&#039;.$empty; </p>
<p>$cats = get_categories(&quot;show_count=1&amp;use_desc_for_title=0&amp;hierarchical=0$hide_empty&quot;); </p>
<p>$filteredCats = array(); </p>
<p>foreach ($cats as $cat) {<br />
if ($cat-&gt;count &lt; $minnum || $cat-&gt;count &gt; $maxnum)<br />
continue; </p>
<p>array_push($filteredCats, $cat);<br />
} </p>
<p>$tagscats = array_merge($tags, $filteredCats);</p>
				
				<p>
									</p>
		
		</div>
		
		<cite>
		
		Posted by <span class="commentauthor">Ray</span> | <a href="#comment-4075" title="">March 20, 2010, 10:49 pm</a> 						
		
		</cite>
		
		
		</li>
		
	
	
